data.description:
THIS HOME IS A MUST SEE!  
Beautiful home like new, ready to move in.  South end location.  Has 4 bedrooms upstairs and 2 full bathrooms, laundry room, large landing.  Master has 2 walk in closets, dual sinks, separate shower and tub.  Den/Office downstairs with 1/2 bath.  Back yard ready for your landscaping.  Patio slab at back sliding door.  Too much to list! Just cleaned from top to bottom..  MOVE IN READY for just over $150.00 per square foot.  Cheaper than mobile homes.   MUST SELL ASAP  MAKE ANY REASONABLE OFFER!!
